Belgian'''Belgia''' or '''Belgian''' refer to something or someone of, or related to, '''Belgium'''.It may also refer to:*A person from Belgium, or of Belgian descent. For information about the Belgian people, see Belgians, Demographics of Belgium and Culture of Belgium. For specific persons, see List of Belgians*Belgian language, an extinct language formerly spoken in Gallia Belgica**Belgian Dutch and Belgian French, variants of Dutch and French, respectively*Belgian (horse), breed of heavy horse*Belgian cuisine*Belgian waffle, in culinary contexts*SS Belgian, a cargo ship in service with F Leyland ; Co Ltd from 1919 to 1934*SS Belgia, a passenger ship in service with the Gotha Line from 1930 to 1941See also*Special:Allpages/Belgian|List of all pages beginning with "Belgian"